<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Apple Macbook Air M3</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../CSS/ProductDetailsStyles.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>


</head>

<body>

<!--Main container to contain the 2 columns-->
<container class="container">

    <!--Left gallery-->
    <div class="left-column">
        <img src="../../Images/MacbookM3/MacbookAirM3.png" class="thumbnail" id="ProductImg">

        <div class="small-img-row">
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/MacbookM3/MacbookAirM3.png" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/MacbookM3/1.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/MacbookM3/2.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
            <div class="small-img-col">
                <img src="../../Images/MacbookM3/3.jpg" width="100%" class="small-img">
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <hr class="vertical-line"/>

    <!--Right product info and stuff-->
    <div class="right-column">
        <h1 class="name">HP Spectre x360</h1>
        <h3 class="price">Rs.100000</h3>

        <!--In stock/out of stock square thingy-->
        <div class="availability">In Stock</div>

        <!--Product details table-->
        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <td>Brand</td>
                <td>Apple</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Model Name</td>
                <td>Macbook Air M3</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Storage Capacity</td>
                <td>512 GB</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>CPU</td>
                <td>M3</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Memory</td>
                <td>8 GB</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="option-buttons">
            <button class="buy-now">Buy Now</button>
            <button class="add-to-cart">Add to Cart</button>
        </div>

        <div class="favourite">
            <i id="wishlist-icon" class="far fa-star"></i><p>Wishlist</p>
        </div>

        <p class="description">The MacBook Air M3 is a lightweight and powerful laptop designed for users who demand top-tier performance in a sleek package. Powered by Apple's latest M3 chip, it offers exceptional speed and efficiency for multitasking, creative work, and running resource-intensive applications. The laptop features a 13.3-inch Retina display with True Tone technology for vibrant colors and sharp visuals. Its fanless design ensures silent operation and long-lasting battery life for all-day use. The MacBook Air M3 includes advanced security features such as Touch ID for secure logins and data protection. With a backlit Magic Keyboard, spacious trackpad, and a variety of ports for connectivity, the MacBook Air M3 is perfect for on-the-go professionals and students.
        </p>
    </div>

</container>

<script src="../../JS/ProductDetailsScript.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
